---
title: Spicy Chicken Enchilada Pasta with Zucchini & Sour Cream
description: It’s a magnificent mashup only our chefs could dream up: enchilada pasta! We've replace the tortillas with tender penne tossed in creamy enchilada sauce with sautéed zucchini. Top the pasta with a garlicky chicken cutlet, and finish with a drizzle of sour cream and a shower of zingy scallion greens for a supremely delicious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b310ff2ccb8b03ddc0f2b3-2444ea25.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67b310ff2ccb8b03ddc0f2b3-en-US.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 670 kcal
